```plantuml
@startuml quasirsg_Henry-M3

actor User
participant "Express App" as Express
participant "Middleware (body-parser)" as Middleware
participant "Route Handler" as Route
participant "Custom $Promise" as Promise
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Express: HTTP Request (POST /data)
Express -> Middleware: Parse request body
Middleware --> Express: Parsed data
Express -> Route: Forward request
Route -> Promise: Create new Promise
Promise -> DB: Async query
DB --> Promise: Query result
Promise --> Route: Resolve/Reject
Route --> Express: Send response
Express --> User: HTTP Response

@enduml
```